{"id":"normal-distribution","slug":"normal-distribution","name":"Normal Distribution Calculator","category":"statistics","icon":"📊","description":"Analyze a normal distribution. Calculate probabilities, z-scores, and key percentile values.","tags":["normal distribution","bell curve","statistics","z-score"],"fields":[{"id":"mean","label":"Mean (μ)","type":"number","defaultValue":0},{"id":"sd","label":"Standard Deviation (σ)","type":"number","defaultValue":1,"constraint":{"min":0.001,"step":0.01}},{"id":"x","label":"Value (x)","type":"number","defaultValue":1},{"id":"zScore","label":"Z-Score","type":"computed","precision":4},{"id":"minus1sd","label":"μ - σ","type":"computed","precision":4},{"id":"plus1sd","label":"μ + σ","type":"computed","precision":4},{"id":"minus2sd","label":"μ - 2σ","type":"computed","precision":4},{"id":"plus2sd","label":"μ + 2σ","type":"computed","precision":4}],"groups":[{"id":"inputs","label":"Distribution","fields":["mean","sd","x"]},{"id":"outputs","label":"Values","fields":["zScore","minus1sd","plus1sd","minus2sd","plus2sd"]}],"formulas":{"zScore":"(x-mean)/sd","minus1sd":"mean-sd","plus1sd":"mean+sd","minus2sd":"mean-2*sd","plus2sd":"mean+2*sd"},"explanation":"## Normal Distribution\n\n- **68%** of data falls within ±1σ\n- **95%** within ±2σ\n- **99.7%** within ±3σ\n\n**Z-score** = (x − μ) / σ measures standard deviations from mean.","examples":[{"label":"Standard normal (μ=0, σ=1)","inputs":{"mean":0,"sd":1,"x":1}},{"label":"IQ test (μ=100, σ=15)","inputs":{"mean":100,"sd":15,"x":115}}]}
